wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Wes-Stretlin-2024-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/08/Wes-Stretlin-2024-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>据报道， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/puddle-of-mudd">Puddle of Mudd</a>主唱韦斯·斯坎特林 (Wes Scantlin) 在与警方对峙后被捕并被喷洒胡椒喷雾。</p><p>据<a href="https://www.tmz.com/2024/08/03/puddle-mudd-wes-scantlin-arrested-swat-standoff-swat-pepper-balls/"><em>TMZ</em></a>报道，斯坎特林于周三（7 月 31 日）因交通违规在交通站被捕，警方发现这位歌手对之前在机场持有武器的案件持有有效逮捕令。</p><p>然而，当斯坎特林被命令下车时，他没有遵守。报道称，在危机谈判代表和喷雾剂未能将他哄出车外后，特警队于凌晨 4 点被叫来打破车窗并发射非致命胡椒球。斯坎特林随后显然投降并下了车。</p><p>据报道，斯坎特林被送往医院，眼睛被胡椒球弄得通红，但没有受到任何其他伤害。</p><p>这位后垃圾摇滚乐队的主唱因未遂逮捕令而被立案，并因拒捕而受到新指控。他现已获释，并将于 8 月 20 日出庭<em>。NME</em>已联系 Scantlin 的公关寻求评论。 </p><figure id="attachment_3038667" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3038667" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3038667" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Puddle-Of-Mudd-Wes-Scantlin.jpg" alt="泥泞的水坑" width="2000" height="1269" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Puddle-Of-Mudd-Wes-Scantlin.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Puddle-Of-Mudd-Wes-Scantlin-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Puddle-Of-Mudd-Wes-Scantlin-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Puddle-Of-Mudd-Wes-Scantlin-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Puddle-Of-Mudd-Wes-Scantlin-1392x883.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/09/Puddle-Of-Mudd-Wes-Scantlin-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3038667" class="wp-caption-text">韦斯·斯坎特林 (Wes Scantlin) 是《泥坑》中的一员。图片来源：Brigitte Engl/Redferns</figcaption></figure><p>斯坎特林此前曾于<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/puddle-mudd-singer-arrested-gun-charges-2139509">2017 年因涉嫌持枪试图登机而</a>被捕。</p><p>随后，他在洛杉矶国际机场因携带 BB 枪而被捕，当时他试图登上飞往德克萨斯州凯勒的航班，乐队原定在该地的布朗森摇滚场地演出。目前尚不清楚斯坎特林的未决逮捕令是否与该具体案件有关。</p><p>在其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/puddle-of-mudds-wes-scantlin-admits-infamous-nirvana-cover-looked-and-sounded-like-total-shit-3369672">韦斯·斯坎特林 (Wes Scantlin) 承认 Puddle of Mudd 臭名昭著的 Nirvana 封面“看起来和听起来都完全是狗屎”。</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/puddle-of-mudd-frontman-wes-scantlin-arrested-and-pepper-sprayed-after-police-stand-off-3780789">《Puddle of Mudd》主唱韦斯·斯坎特林 (Wes Scantlin) 在与警方对峙后被捕并被喷胡椒水，该消息</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">《NME》</a>上。</p> ;
